<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Acceso denegado</title>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .error-container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      padding: 60px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 20px;
    }
    .error-title {
      color: #ef4444;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
    }
    .error-message {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .btn-home {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: none;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-home:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1d4ed8 0%, #1e40af 100%);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
    }
    .error-icon {
      font-size: 72px;
      color: #ef4444;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <i class="material-icons error-icon">block</i>
    <h3 class="error-title">403</h3>
    <p class="error-message">No tienes permisos para acceder a esta p√°gina.</p>
    <a href="/signin" class="btn btn-home waves-effect waves-light">
      <i class="material-icons left">home</i>Volver al inicio
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
